==English==

===Etymology===
See [[English]] and [[bond]]

===Noun===
'''[[English]] [[bond]]'''
# In [[bricklaying]], an arrangement of bricks such that one [[course]] has the [[short]] sides of the bricks ([[header]]s) facing outwards, and the next course has the [[long]] sides of the bricks ([[stretcher]]s) facing outwards.

